{
  "stem": "19111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 225.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I have witnesses-- witnessed father and son actually choking each other because one thought that he got a, a tiny little bit more bread than the other in his ration.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was, well, if you want to compare it to animals, I think animals have more instinct than, than, than the way we were meant-- made to feel.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- all reality has disappeared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You live for that moment and for that little piece of bread that you can get.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, sometimes I wonder-- I ask myself the question, how the heck did I survive all that?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what happened to us-- my father and myself, we were still together at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we went out to work for the small company, many times we had to work even at night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were night shift and day shifts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and the night shift-- when we worked the night shift, we-- the Germans-- not the soldiers, but there were other supervisors and other people-- engineers and other people, civilians-- used to come and supervise the job.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and they had their rucksack or the backpack with their lunches and their food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were hanging on a chair because these factories were being built inside the woods.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was so starved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was so hungry that there were times where I saw that, where he hung up his backpack, and I knew there was food in there.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
